  RFC8114 [label="RFC8114
Delivery of IPv4 Multicast Services to
IPv4 Clients over an IPv6 Multicast
Network
2017", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="This document specifies a solution for the delivery of IPv4 multicast services to IPv4 clients over an IPv6 multicast network.  The solution relies upon a stateless IPv4-in-IPv6 encapsulation scheme and uses an IPv6 multicast distribution tree to deliver IPv4 multicast traffic.  The solution is particularly useful for the delivery of multicast service offerings to customers serviced by Dual-Stack Lite (DS-Lite).", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

